# HaGeZi's Threat Intelligence Feeds DNS Blocklist
# A blocklist for blocking malware, cryptojacking, scam, spam and phishing.
# Blocks domains known to spread malware, launch phishing attacks and host command-and-control servers.
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hagezi/dns-blocklists/main/adblock/tif.txt

# Dandelion Sprout's Anti-Malware List
